[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "二人とも、来てくれてありがとう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01079",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "ナナに呼ばれて来ない兄はいない！\nリーベもそうだろう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01080",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "今日といい先日の食事会といい、ヴァレリアはいつも\n突然ですね。私にも予定があるのですが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01081",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ごめんってリーベ。\n兄弟のことで、早く二人に話を聞きたくて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01082",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "おお、兄弟の話か！　なんでも聞いてくれ！\nナナが兄弟に興味を示してくれて兄は嬉しいぞ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01083",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "先日の様子から推察するに、\nヘルト兄様についてでしょうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01084",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "その通り！　さっすがリーベ。\n話が早くて助かるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01085",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私、ヘルトが何を考えているのか、\nどういう人なのか、知りたいの！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01086",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そうすれば、ヘルトを元気づける方法が\n分かるかもしれないから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01087",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "なるほど。それで、私たち兄弟から\nヘルト兄様の話を聞こうと考えているのですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01088",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "おお……兄は今、猛烈に感動している！\nこの思いやりこそ、理想的な兄弟の形じゃないか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01089",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "果ての大陸へたどり着くためにヘルト兄様の力は\n不可欠と考えますので、私も協力しましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01090",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "……それに、私もゴゥ兄様も、\n今のヘルト兄様のことが心配ですから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01091",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ありがとう！　早速だけど、二人から見たヘルトの\n印象とか、思い出話とかあったら聞きたいわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01092",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "ヘルト兄様は強く、\n私たち兄弟を先導してくれる頼れる方だ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01093",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "まだ私たちの戦闘技術がおぼつかない頃、\nヘルト兄様が自ら、私たちを鍛えてくれたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01094",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "兄様は兄弟一人一人の本質や特徴を理解した上で\nそこを伸ばすための特訓を行ってくださいました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01095",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ただ、少しでも気に入らないことがあると\nすぐ投げ出したりお仕置きと称した攻撃をしてきたり",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01096",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "シトリンは特にお仕置きを受けていたな。反対に、\nリーベはあまり叱られていなかったような……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01097",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ヘルト兄様が叱るのには理由があります。\n叱られない立ち回りをすればいいのです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01098",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "兄様は、怠惰であることや、\n能力を活かさないことに対して厳しい方ですから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01099",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "確かに、シトリンは兄様の特訓をめんどくさがって\nさぼってたからな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01100",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あはは、シトリンがさぼるの、なんか想像できるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01101",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ヘルト兄様に叱られることに関しては\nヴァレリアも他人事ではありませんでしたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01102",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "えっ！　私！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01103",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "特訓後、お腹が空いたと言ったヴァレリアが、\nヘルト兄様のお肉をゼロ姉様と共謀して盗み食いし――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01104",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "妹を庇い、その咎を負ったゴゥ兄様が\nお仕置きされるのは、もはや日常茶飯事でした",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01105",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ご、ごめんね、お兄ちゃん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01106",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "かわいい妹のためだ、なんてことはない！\nそれに兄様はお仕置きの際いつもこう言っていた――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01107",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "「こそこそ盗み取っているのが気に食わない」と。\nつまり、次は正面から取りに行けばいい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01108",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そ、そういう問題なのかしら……？\nどちらにせよ、盗むのはよくないんじゃ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01109",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ヘルト兄様は実力主義なところがありますから。\n正面から勝ち取れば問題はなさそうです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01110",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "えぇ……難しいわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01111",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "まぁ、ヘルト兄様には難しいところもあるが――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01112",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "兄弟の面倒ごとを引き受けたり、まとめてくれたり、\n私たち兄弟のために動いてくれる一面もある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01113",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "そうだろう、ナナ！　お前も昔、魔物に襲われて\n危ないところをヘルト兄様に助けられたじゃないか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01114",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ヴァレリアは記憶を失っているのですから\n分かるわけないでしょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01115",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うん。悪いけど覚えてないわ。\nでも――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01116",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ありがとう。二人のおかげでヘルトについて\nまたちょっと分かった気がする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01117",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私たち兄弟って、\nケンカするくらいには仲良かったのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01118",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ケンカ……あれは一方的な蹂躙のようでも\nありましたが、ものは言いようですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01119",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "他の兄弟にも話を聞いてくるわ。\nよかったらまた、思い出話聞かせてね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01120",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "ああ、もちろんだ！\nいつでも聞きに来るんだぞ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01121",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ヘルトって、私たちの面倒を見てくれたりして、\n　ちゃんとお兄ちゃんっぽいところもあったのね）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01122",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ゴゥとリーベは、ヘルトを兄として見ているみたい\n　だけど、他のみんなはどうなのかしら）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01123",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]